Expected Differences
--------------------

Accuracy: Point 1 and 2 must be made, otherwise te results will be wrong for
          Mercator map projection ans sfc_assi_options=2.

          Point 3 is also neessary, otherwise the strange increments of q
          will be generated for the single OBS tests.

          Point 4 is also necessary, otherwise with a wrong time FG, the 
          3D-Var job will be terminated normally with no errors reported.

          Point 5 is not only special for CWB data, but also can save the
          computing when SSMI Tb not assimilated.
       
CPU/memory:  CPU and memory should not be changed

